-- =================================================================
-- DIGITAL DIRECTORY — SEED DATA: 100 fictional influencer profiles
-- All personas are FICTIONAL. Any resemblance to real people is
-- coincidental. Run in Supabase SQL Editor.
--
-- HOW IT WORKS (important):
--   profiles.id has a FK to auth.users(id), so we must create auth
--   users first. Your on_auth_user_created trigger then auto-creates
--   the profile rows, which we UPDATE with the seed content.
--   Seed users cannot log in (no valid password hash).
--
-- CLEANUP: delete from auth.users where email like 'seed-%@example.com';
--   (cascades through profiles -> all child tables)
-- =================================================================
