  ('f2a450d0-f078-403f-b956-5db353494d97', 'Stargazing from Seattle: a light pollution survival guide', 'City skies hide almost everything, but not quite everything. What you can actually see from a rooftop in Seattle, the two-hour drive that changes the sky completely, and the beginner telescope I recommend every single time.'),
  ('f2a450d0-f078-403f-b956-5db353494d97', 'Why reusable rockets changed everything', 'Launch cost per kilogram is the whole ballgame. Reusability turned rockets from ammunition into aircraft, and the downstream effects — constellations, cheap science missions, lunar logistics — are still compounding. A propulsion engineer''s view of the next decade of spaceflight.'),
  ('df977c50-8b88-4e5a-9599-b1671c85c4a2', 'Fermentation basics every home cook should know', 'Salt, time and patience: fermentation is the cheapest flavor upgrade in cooking. Start with quick pickles, graduate to hot sauce, then attempt miso. Ratios, jars, safety and the troubleshooting chart I wish I had when my first batch went sideways.'),
  ('df977c50-8b88-4e5a-9599-b1671c85c4a2', 'Eating my way through Mexico City', 'Forty-eight hours, eleven meals, zero regrets. A chef''s eating itinerary for Mexico City: the market breakfast, the noodle counter with no sign, the dessert worth the queue. What I stole for my own menu and the technique I am still practicing.'),
  ('3eb8665a-427a-4c84-ae53-fa19241152c7', 'Training on the road without losing progress', 'Hotel gyms have two dumbbells and a broken cable machine. Fine. A traveling strength template: push, pull, hinge, squat, carry — thirty minutes, any equipment. I used it across Cape Town and Austin and came home stronger.'),
  ('3eb8665a-427a-4c84-ae53-fa19241152c7', 'The boring fundamentals that actually work', 'No secret protocol: progressive overload, protein, eight thousand steps, sleep. I tracked a year of training data to prove the boring stuff compounds. Charts and the three exercises I will never drop.'),
  ('aff98803-3046-4cd3-b549-58d61f49d7ef', 'Why I switched my entire desk setup', 'New year, new studio. I rebuilt my desk setup around an ultrawide monitor, a custom mechanical keyboard and a proper audio interface. Cable management took a full day. Here is every product I kept, everything I returned, and what I would buy again for a video editing workflow.'),
  ('67ec8773-fcfe-4058-893c-09d2f22a6bfe', 'Recovery is the real training', 'Everyone sees the ninety minutes. Nobody sees the ice baths, sleep tracking, mobility work and nutrition that make them possible. My full recovery protocol after a Champions League away trip to Paris: cold exposure, compression, carbs timing and why I stopped scrolling at night.'),
  ('67ec8773-fcfe-4058-893c-09d2f22a6bfe', 'What academy football taught me about pressure', 'I signed my first academy contract at thirteen. The pitch teaches you fast: talent gets you noticed, habits keep you employed. Notes for young footballers on trials, setbacks and the season everything clicked.'),
  ('3b14dd8b-ae0b-4ef9-a18a-14fb30f4f705', 'Why I switched my entire desk setup', 'New year, new studio. I rebuilt my desk setup around an ultrawide monitor, a custom mechanical keyboard and a proper audio interface. Cable management took a full day. Here is every product I kept, everything I returned, and what I would buy again for a video editing workflow.'),
  ('fb8fd26e-9ca9-4d59-8f8d-2ad7c42ba9d3', 'The indie games I could not stop playing this year', 'Big budgets buy fidelity; small teams buy ideas. My favorite indies this year: a puzzle game about maps, a roguelike about tea, a platformer made by two people in Tokyo. Demos linked for all of them.'),
  ('cfe254ca-0e8a-4e5a-b973-8268a8472c7f', 'Recovery is the real training', 'Everyone sees the ninety minutes. Nobody sees the ice baths, sleep tracking, mobility work and nutrition that make them possible. My full recovery protocol after a Champions League away trip to Barcelona: cold exposure, compression, carbs timing and why I stopped scrolling at night.'),
  ('cfe254ca-0e8a-4e5a-b973-8268a8472c7f', 'What academy football taught me about pressure', 'I signed my first academy contract at thirteen. The pitch teaches you fast: talent gets you noticed, habits keep you employed. Notes for young footballers on trials, setbacks and the season everything clicked.'),
  ('f78c3b0c-c762-48b4-a0f3-fd5cba05f7cc', 'My live rig, explained', 'People ask what is on stage: a laptop I do not trust, a synth I love, and a mixer that saved three shows. Full signal chain, redundancy plan and the soundcheck ritual I never skip.'),
  ('f78c3b0c-c762-48b4-a0f3-fd5cba05f7cc', 'Recording an album on tour', 'Hotel rooms are terrible studios and perfect ones. I tracked vocals in Buenos Aires, synths in London, and mixed everything on headphones on night trains. Gear list, gain staging on the move, and why constraints made the record better.'),
  ('f296ce1f-d9b6-4953-ab13-d2b25b3c3a35', 'Why I switched my entire desk setup', 'New year, new studio. I rebuilt my desk setup around an ultrawide monitor, a custom mechanical keyboard and a proper audio interface. Cable management took a full day. Here is every product I kept, everything I returned, and what I would buy again for a video editing workflow.'),
  ('f296ce1f-d9b6-4953-ab13-d2b25b3c3a35', 'My 2022 smartphone camera shootout', 'I spent six weeks comparing flagship smartphone cameras in Berlin and Seoul: low light, portrait mode, video stabilization and RAW photography. The gap between computational photography pipelines keeps narrowing, but color science still separates the leaders. Full test methodology, sample galleries and my pick for creators inside.'),
  ('2a37d7d6-f0be-44f5-98e9-fd69747e460a', 'What a year of filming one street taught me', 'I planted a camera on one street in Buenos Aires for a year: the barber, the night bakery, the retired boxer who feeds cats at dawn. Documentary filmmaking is mostly waiting, then all at once. Festival plans and three scenes that almost broke me.'),
  ('2a37d7d6-f0be-44f5-98e9-fd69747e460a', 'Editing is rewriting', 'The film you shot is not the film you have. In the edit, scenes swap meaning, silence outperforms dialogue and your favorite shot dies first. My editing process from assembly to picture lock, with timelines as proof.'),
  ('eab8cd68-0ed7-4b22-a192-07ca7d6005a3', 'Why I still shoot film', 'Film photography slows me down in the best way. Thirty-six frames force intention; digital invites hoarding. My hybrid workflow: 35mm for personal work in Hong Kong, mirrorless for assignments, one contact sheet review every Sunday.'),
  ('eab8cd68-0ed7-4b22-a192-07ca7d6005a3', 'Street photography etiquette in Hong Kong', 'One month shooting street photography in Hong Kong. Lessons: shoot with your feet, ask with your eyes, and learn ten words of the local language. Camera settings for fast light, my favorite focal length, and why I deleted half the archive. The best photographs happened while waiting for other photographs.'),
  ('89a4cc95-7edf-499e-bc70-ed9ffce58884', 'Film study: how guards create space', 'Watched two hundred clips of pick-and-roll coverage this month. The best guards manipulate the second defender, not the first. Breakdowns of hesitation dribbles, snake dribbles and why shooting gravity changes everything about spacing in modern basketball.'),
