  ('c3e8bb8c-929a-40bc-9f93-bad17d70a925', 'Notes on AI scaling in 2025', 'Everyone asks whether AI scaling laws are hitting a wall. After a year of training runs and inference optimization, my read: raw pretraining gains are slowing, but post-training, tool use and agent orchestration are compounding fast. GPU clusters, data quality and evaluation infrastructure matter more than parameter count now.'),
