  ('2f38ffdc-2c49-4924-af66-fdb2da435c4c', 'My 2022 smartphone camera shootout', 'I spent six weeks comparing flagship smartphone cameras in Tokyo and New York: low light, portrait mode, video stabilization and RAW photography. The gap between computational photography pipelines keeps narrowing, but color science still separates the leaders. Full test methodology, sample galleries and my pick for creators inside.'),
